metadata.description: 2324 Nyan Doge Collection, featuring hand-drawn animated pixel artwork brought to life by a Singapore NFT artist. The Nyan has become a global internet phenomenon. Don't miss your chance to own a piece of Internet history today! This is somethings notable. Holder of Genesis Nyan Doge will get exclusive access and drop for coming multichains's Nyan Doge.
